nodes.text: Lillea Bringbit was a Human female from Coruscant. She was a regular patron of the Outlander Club on Coruscant. She witnessed Jedi Anakin Skywalker's fall from bounty hunter Zam Wesell's speeder.
Lillea Bringbit was portrayed by Gillian Libbert who stood next to another female Outlander Club patron played by co-worker Julie D'Antoni. Lillea Bringbit is also an anagram of Gillian Libbert.
